<section title="Charts">
<p>To create a chart or graph with data from a Mingle project(s), you can use a <cref topic="macro_reference">Mingle macro</cref>. You can either 1) hand-type the macro by clicking the orange Mingle icon on the editing toolbar or 2) insert a template macro using the <cref topic="mingle_macro_builder">Macro Builder</cref>.</p>
<hint>See <cref topic="mingle_tips_and_tricks">Mingle tips and tricks</cref> for hints on macro syntax, chart layout and chart sizing, and using project variables in charts.</hint> 
